data.description: Best Buy!  Peace and Privacy in your own Oasis.  Many possibilities, multigenerational living, Air BNB, room to grow on .59 acres  for all your toys or other equipment. This beautiful 4 bedroom, 1 3/4 bath daylight basement rambler has all the bells and whistles.  Newly remodeled kitchen with granite countertops and upgraded stainless steel appliances.  fireplaces newly redone.  Custom electronic blinds. Refurbished hardwood floors throughout.  Upgraded light fixtures.  New flooring on deck.  Main bath has granite countertops with deluxe shower.   Newer furnace with air conditioning.  Newer hot water tank. New plumbing. Shed in backyard.
